title: Will Your Team Surprise... or Flop?
itunes:title: Will Your Team Surprise... or Flop?
description:
A room filled with some heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Colleen Wolfe, & Dave Dameshek – discuss all the latest news from around the NFL including Julian Edelman's new deal with the Patriots, the Jets' plans to release or trade Eric Decker, and the Ravens parting ways with Dennis Pitta. The heroes also discuss which hyped up teams are most likely to stumble and which overlooked teams are most likely to surprise in 2017.
